ive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26|quote=Muharram 1428 - Kensington Town Hall London - January 2007 - Sayyid Qasim al-Jalali - Haj Basim Karbalaei}}</ref>\n|London, UK\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kuQ_zBMB0cE&t=49s ''Ya Galbi Ya Sabir'']\n|-\n|2008\n|1429\n|Husayniyat al-Qasab\n|Manama, Bahrain\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V5bPE3FAvXo ''Ilahi Rid Gharib al-Dar'']\n|-\n|2009 (Jan)\n|1430\n|Husayniyat al-Rasool al-Adham - al-Karbalaeia<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090401075240/http://alkarbalaeia.net/media/index.php?main_page=song&cPath=100_126&sPath=406|title=Haj Basim al-Karbalaei - Muharram 1430 AH|last=|first=|date=2009-04-01|website=alkarbalaeia.net|language=ar|via=web.archive.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|Kuwait\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E0oHiNfvALk ''Yahssain Awal Ma Habeyna'']\n|-\n|2009 (Dec)\n|1431\n|Husayniyat al-Rasool al-Adham - al-Karbalaeia<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329222243/http://www.karbala-london.org/muharam1431/index.php|title=Muharram 1431 - Sheikh Rashad al-Ansari - Haj Basim Karbalaei|last=|first=|date=2010-03-29|website=karbala-london.org|via=web.archive.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|London, UK\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ywhh5MHUwD8 ''Ashofak Kil Fajir'']\n|-\n|2010\n|1432\n|Husayniyat al-Rasool al-Adham - al-Karbalaeia<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101212155633/http://www.alkarbalaeia.net/media/index.php?main_page=song&cPath=100_126&sPath=470|title=Haj Basim al-Karbalaei - Muharram 1432 AH|last=|first=|date=2010-12-12|website=alkarbalaeia.net|language=ar|via=web.archive.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|Kuwait\n|''\u0650[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IuXWODy3s8I Ana al-Qahir]''\n|-\n|2011\n|1433\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212021902/http://www.alashoor.net/baseem-1433.htm|title=al-Radood al-Haj Basim al-Karbalaei - Muharram 1433|last=|first=|date=2012-02-12|website=alashoor.net|language=ar|via=web.archive.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|[[Basra]], [[Iraq]]\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_PMkmGZ-yI ''Dumti Karbala'']\n|-\n|2012\n|1434\n|Husayniyat Ashor\n|Kuwait\n|''[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZNsmv1mlOI Ghadhab Rab al-Ibad]''\n|-\n|2013\n|1435\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor\n|Basra, Iraq\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wWDTJ4Wu7uw ''La Tinsa al-Wasiya'']\n|-\n|2014\n|1436\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor\n|Basra, Iraq\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6mMf-rm-jdQ ''Kil Ma Ashoofak'']\n|-\n|2015\n|1437\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor\n|Basra, Iraq\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IdjRzHSW3aY ''Gooman Banat al-Nabi'']\n|-\n|2016\n|1438\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor\n|Basra, Iraq\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VsxYo8jLMwQ ''Yuma Atamnich Alaya'']\n|-\n|2017\n|1439\n|Husayniyat Dawood al-Ashoor\n|Basra, Iraq\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l7WIn7ydCDY ''Yabu Fadhil'']\n|-\n|2018\n|1440\n|Al-Akbar Foundation<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alakbarfoundation.com/muharram/muharram-majlis-2018-%e2%80%a2-1440/|title=Muharram Majlis 2018/1440 - Sayid Hussain al-Modarresi {{!}} Haj Basim Karbalaei|last=|first=|date=|website=Al-Akbar Foundation|language=en-GB|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|London, UK\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A9qrszKBEGE ''Beyn al-Mehdi Wil Abbas'']\n|-\n|2019\n|1441\n|Al-Akbar Foundation/Dewan al-Kafeel\n|London, UK\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZW2zC-HMeXU ''Ballah Ya Nahar'']\n|}\n\n== Discography ==\n==== Studio Albums ====\n\n*''Wa Fatimatah'' (O Fatima) (1993) [Um al-Banin Foundation]\n*''Wa Tabqa Lana'' (It Remains For Us) (2000) [Um al-Banin Foundation]\n*''Ya Hussain'' (O' Husayn) (2002) [Karbala Records]\n*''Labayk Ya Husayn'' (Here We Are O' Husayn) (2003) [Karbala Records]\n*''